description: AMUNDI S&P 500 UCITS ETF - DAILY HEDGED EUR seeks to replicate as closely as possible the S&P 500 Index in Euros, whether the trend is rising or falling and has a monthly currency hedging in EUR. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to the 500 largest stocks on the US market, with a single transaction. The S&P 500 is recognised as the leading benchmark index of the US market. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi S&P 500 UCITS ETF - DAILY HEDGED EUR (C)
